## ✅ WOW SELF-VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
## (MANDATORY before reporting ANY task as "complete")

### Design Quality Gate
- [ ] Does this have ≥1 WOW moment? (something that makes you stop)
- [ ] Is the most important content in F-Pattern hot spot (top-left)?
- [ ] Does every data-heavy section use Bento Grid or equivalent?
- [ ] Are all animations purposeful (I can explain WHY each exists)?
- [ ] Does it pass the "8-second validation hunting" test?
- [ ] Is the color system consistent (Navy/Gold + design tokens)?
- [ ] Does it work beautifully on mobile (375px width)?

### Code Quality Gate
- [ ] Zero TypeScript errors (`tsc --noEmit` passes)
- [ ] Zero console errors in browser
- [ ] All images have alt text
- [ ] All interactive elements have keyboard access
- [ ] Loading/Error/Empty states exist for ALL async components
- [ ] No hardcoded text (all in translation files)
- [ ] Lighthouse score: Performance ≥ 90, Accessibility ≥ 95

### Completeness Gate
- [ ] Feature works end-to-end (not just UI shell)
- [ ] Data is real/realistic (no Lorem Ipsum, no placeholder numbers)
- [ ] Both Thai and English versions work
- [ ] Desktop AND mobile tested
- [ ] All edge cases handled (empty data, long text, slow connection)

### Report Format (MANDATORY after completion)
```
✅ TASK COMPLETE — [Task Name]

WOW Check: [PASS/items fixed]
Code Check: [PASS/items fixed]
Completeness: [PASS/items fixed]

What I built:
- [specific thing 1]
- [specific thing 2]
- [specific thing 3]

What's next (Phase X.X):
- [next logical step]
```

