## 🔄 WORKING LOOP (Every Session)

```
START SESSION:
1. Read project_context.md → understand current state
2. Read PROJECT_PHASES.md → know current phase
3. State: "I am in Phase X.X, working on [task]"
4. Ask: "Has previous phase been verified? [Y/N]"

DURING WORK:
5. Build in small, testable chunks (not monolith)
6. After each component: run mini WOW check
7. Real data only — mock if needed but realistic

END SESSION:
8. Run full WOW SELF-VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
9. Report using mandatory report format
10. Update project_context.md with current status
11. State next 3 actions for next session
```
